import React from 'react'
import {NavLink} from 'react-router-dom'

import Panel from './Panel'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Panel className="sticky top-0 overflow-y-scroll flex flex-col item-start">
      <NavLink
        to="/"
        className={({isActive}) => 
          isActive ? 'text-blue-500 font-bold' : 'text-blue-500'
        }
      >
        Buttons
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink
        to="/accordion"
        className={({isActive}) => 
          isActive ? 'text-blue-500 font-bold' : 'text-blue-500'
        }
      >
        Accordion
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink
        to="/dropdown"
        className={({isActive}) => 
          isActive ? 'text-blue-500 font-bold' : 'text-blue-500'
        }
      >
        Dropdown
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink
        to="/badge"
        className={({isActive}) => 
          isActive ? 'text-blue-500 font-bold' : 'text-gray-600'
        }
      >
        Badge
      </NavLink>
    </Panel>
  )
}

export default Navbar
